---
title: Spiced Chicken & Chive Yoghurt with Roast Beetroot, Pumpkin & Parsnip Toss
description: There’s nothing better than chicken that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully charred with mild spices on the outside. That’s how we’re preparing our protein tonight, plus add a drizzle of creamy chive yoghurt to double down on all that flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-spiced-chicken-chive-yoghurt-ab022850.jpg
